## ğŸŒ What Is Infrastructure as Code (IaC)?

Infrastructure as Code (IaC) means managing and provisioning infrastructure through **code** instead of manual configuration via a UI.

Instead of clicking in a cloud console to:

- Configure virtual machines
- Set up networks
- Create firewall rules
- Attach storage
- Define IAM policies

â€¦you write code that defines everything.

The code can be:

- âœ… Version controlled  
- âœ… Reused  
- âœ… Reviewed  
- âœ… Automated  
- âœ… Audited  

> **Your infrastructure becomes software.**

